        <!-- Release notes (keep it brief) -->
        <releasenotes>
            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 2.0.43 - Only Update Furthest During Natural Navigation</h3>

            <h4>Changes</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Don't update furthestSlide during tag jumps (intercept window)</li>
                <li>User didn't VIEW slides during jump, so progress shouldn't increase</li>
                <li>Score from Storyline init reflects load position, not actual progress</li>
                <li>Added logging when ignoring score during tag navigation</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Technical Details</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Check inInterceptWindow before updating furthestSlide</li>
                <li>Only natural navigation (no pending tag jump) updates furthest</li>
                <li>Applies to both SCORM 1.2 and SCORM 2004 handlers</li>
                <li>Prevents false progress increase from init scores</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Previous Version</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>v2.0.42: Restore furthestSlide from sessionStorage on reload</li>
            </ul>
            ]]>
